        "id": "9f526b54-e862-4be8-b611-d5bbb91e7300",
        "position": {
          "x": -140,
          "y": 80
        },
        "content": "# Superconducting Magnet Quench\n\nAt quench onset, the coil resistance rises sharply.\nThe dump resistor safely dissipates stored magnetic energy.\n**L · dI/dt = -R(t) · I**",
        "width": 340,
        "height": 90,
        "fontSize": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "4940fce5-d324-4f32-8ce6-686d43507782",
        "position": {
